  "prompt": "Are there some people who just looks better without makeup than with makeup?",
  "response": "Yes, there are definitely people who look better without makeup than with it. Beauty is highly subjective, and what looks good on one person might not work for another. Some individuals have naturally radiant skin, beautiful features, or a charm that shines through without the need for makeup. Additionally, makeup preferences vary widely; some people prefer a natural look and feel that too much makeup can hide their true features or personality. Ultimately, it's about personal style, comfort, and what makes someone feel most confident and themselves.",
